P37b:	(a)*sqrt(r1) 	= (-a1^3+20*a1)/8
P7:	2 	= 2
P53a:	(a+4)*sqrt(r1) 	= (3*a1^3-28*a1)/8
P53b:	(a-4)*sqrt(r1) 	= (-5*a1^3+68*a1)/8
