P61b:	-4*a+4 	= -a1^2+12
P67a:	(-4*a-3)*sqrt(r1) 	= (a1^3-44*a1)/8
P67b:	(-4*a+3)*sqrt(r1) 	= (7*a1^3-116*a1)/8
